{"TopicId":153198,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"One New Feture","CreatedByName":"Dogemaster","CreatedById":172307,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-08T14:48:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dogemaster","CreatedById":172307,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-08T14:48:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I was thinking... It would be cool if you could actualy walk around and interact with parts inside the spaceship, right? Well, Basicaly it would mean that, upon takeoff, they would be in their seats. Then you push a button to let them out and do science experiments. Or mybe just send them to bed after the exhausting journey...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. I am New to the Forums\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-08T15:47:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wjolcz","CreatedById":39636,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-08T16:08:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, that would be nice. There was a mod that more or less did this. IVAs are kind of pointless. There are a few buttons you can click, but that\u0027s really it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T17:44:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222879754\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481213310\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002239636\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Veeltch\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn \u200E12\u200E/\u200E8\u200E/\u200E2016 at 11:08 AM, Veeltch said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, that would be nice. There was a mod that more or less did this. IVAs are kind of pointless. There are a few buttons you can click, but that\u0027s really it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn fact there was a mod I saw which allowed you to move your kerbals around in each compartment and even move between them. However it\u0027s been a while since I saw that, and I don\u0027t remember the name of it\u0027s even still under development, but it was an awesome idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dogemaster","CreatedById":172307,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T23:05:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222883689\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481478284\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022103726\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZooNamedGames\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, ZooNamedGames said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn fact there was a mod I saw which allowed you to move your kerbals around in each compartment and even move between them. However it\u0027s been a while since I saw that, and I don\u0027t remember the name of it\u0027s even still under development, but it was an awesome idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know that one, it is called enhanced iva. But there you can just fly right out of the ship, which is a little bit unrealistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T23:12:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222884167\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481497528\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172307\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dogemaster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Dogemaster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know that one, it is called enhanced iva. But there you can just fly right out of the ship, which is a little bit unrealistic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust lack of colliders is all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-19T11:07:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis could be cool if there was a way to interact with stuff and do science from IVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-19T16:28:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh, the dreams of KSP I had back in those heady days of 0.18. \u00A0This was one of those dreams.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-22T07:11:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222893110\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221482145671\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/19/2016 at 2:07 PM, NSEP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0and do science from IVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you tried\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/150122-12-part-commander-continued/#comment-2806669\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EPart Commander\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-22T08:27:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222896613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221482390698\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104207\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ser\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Ser said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you tried\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/150122-12-part-commander-continued/#comment-2806669\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EPart Commander\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool! But thats not what i mean. I thought of doing science expiriments that are inside the IVA. Not operating science from outside inside IVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-22T09:05:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222896663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221482395245\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165635\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NSEP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdi